item.title: For free - F0yders Music [OG Instruments]
item.dc:creator: Sunny
item.description:
Man, big sound. Great stuff. I loved the… what would you call it? Whistle wailing instrument? Real cool. Loved the climax/end of your song where it got BASSY. And you do something real freaky deaky with the way you work through lowpass and highpass, leading me in and out of the song. I probably wouldn’t do it twice, but the first time I heard it, it was dooope.

Got me a-clapping.
